	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Zero-page-indexed accesses will wrap within page zero. For instance, the following code will read memory[$0080] into register A:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; ldx #$c0<br />&nbsp; lda $c0,x<br /></div>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


